## ðŸŽ¯ Query Examples

### Products

#### Get All Products
```php
Product::all();
```

#### Get with Pagination
```php
Product::paginate(10);
```

#### Search Products
```php
Product::where('name', 'like', '%lego%')->get();
```

#### Filter by Category
```php
Product::where('category', 'lego')->get();
```

#### Get Featured Products
```php
Product::where('is_featured', true)->get();
```

#### Sort by Price
```php
Product::orderBy('price', 'asc')->get();
```

#### Complex Query
```php
Product::where('category', 'lego')
    ->where('price', '<', 1000000)
    ->where('stock', '>', 0)
    ->orderBy('rating', 'desc')
    ->paginate(10);
```

#### With Soft Deleted
```php
Product::withTrashed()->get();
```

#### Only Soft Deleted
```php
Product::onlyTrashed()->get();
```

#### Restore Soft Deleted
```php
Product::withTrashed()->find($id)->restore();
```

### Users

#### Find by Email
```php
User::where('email', 'test@example.com')->first();
```

#### Create User
```php
User::create([
    'name' => 'John Doe',
    'email' => 'john@example.com',
    'password' => bcrypt('password123')
]);
```
